{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban advertising of vapes other than on packaging",
        "additional_details": "I believe vape addiction is a plague on my generation, it financially drains us and could seriously damage our lives as the long-term effects of vaping are still largely unknown. Walking down the street, I see hoards of advertisements. Banning these signs along with other types of advertising could help reduce the sales of vapes and free us from this issue.",
        "background": "Some advertising of vapes is permitted. I believe that any advertising of vapes, except on the packaging of vapes themselves, should be banned.",
